text.tspan: Change in vanhanen's Index of Democracy, 1820 to 2000
The Vanhanen's Index of Democracy is produced by combining data on political participation and electoral
competition. Specifically: Index = (% of the adult population who voted in the elections) * (100 - % of the winning
party's votes in a national election)/100
